text: Agnyphantes is a genus of dwarf spiders that was first described by J. E. Hull in 1932. it contains only two species: A. arboreus and A. expunctus. ==See also== * List of Linyphiidae species ==References== Category:Araneomorphae genera Category:Linyphiidae Category:Palearctic spiders Category:Spiders of North America
title: Agnyphantes
